				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/B%E1%BA%AFc-Th%C3%A0nh-ho%E1%BA%A3-tai-ng%E1%BA%ABu-k%E1%BB%B7-nh%E1%BB%8B-tuy%E1%BB%87t-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-3xRi-s-jXe76Tf5ClTBnwA">Bắc Thành hoả tai, ngẫu kỷ nhị tuyệt kỳ 2 - 北城火灾偶紀二絕其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/author-geNjG6kbAxWPLaqdF181sQ">Phan Huy Ích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%C4%83ng/C%E1%BB%95-th%E1%BB%83-thi-nh%E1%BA%A5t-th%E1%BB%A7-ho%E1%BA%A1-Tri%E1%BB%81u-Ti%C3%AAn-qu%E1%BB%91c-s%E1%BB%A9-L%C3%BD-%C4%90%E1%BA%A9u-Phong-k%C3%BD-gi%E1%BA%A3n-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-thi%C3%AAn/poem-dufjwR7ke5zeT0Pc19PDnw">Cổ thể thi nhất thủ hoạ Triều Tiên quốc sứ Lý Đẩu Phong ký giản trường thiên - 古體詩一首和朝鮮國使李斗峰寄柬長篇</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%C4%83ng/author-9vK1MaRfv_HUDMyHo1xP_w">Nguyễn Đăng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/N%E1%BA%A1p-T%C3%A2n/D%C4%A9nh-Ch%C3%A2u-l%C3%A3o-%C3%B4ng-ca/poem-sMaN29nfwosLLi7BpB4dYg">Dĩnh Châu lão ông ca - 穎州老翁歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/N%E1%BA%A1p-T%C3%A2n/author-0SVWGWsIUnN7yr-6nBm82Q">Nạp Tân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/%C4%90%E1%BB%91i-t%E1%BB%ADu/poem-MKcAFb4683ixwnLA8LL3hg">Đối tửu - 對酒</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Mao-Tr%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%90%C3%B4ng/H%E1%BA%A1-t%C3%A2n-lang-%C4%90%E1%BB%99c-s%E1%BB%AD/poem-GdZy4Dk_mBC8Y1dcLVgJaQ">Hạ tân lang - Độc sử - 賀新郎—讀史</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Mao-Tr%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%90%C3%B4ng/author-h4yM6-N0eITEQqfS6Lh1ag">Mao Trạch Đông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-An-qu%E1%BA%ADn-v%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Ho%C3%A0ng-nh%E1%BB%8B-t%E1%BB%AD-th%C6%B0-trai-nguy%C3%AAn-t%E1%BB%8Bch-h%E1%BB%99i-%